More bad news by the way - a Player's Blots are equal to the sum total
of Indulgence POs that have been executed minus those of that number
that have been disputed or vacated. What's missing is Indulgence POs
that have been _satisfied_, which is a serious bug; a Player who has
paid off eir Indulgence Debt is nevertheless Blotted. Also I think P/C
breaks Unity Vote, but those are the only problems I could find with
P/C other than the Big One, and for such a paradigm-upsetting reform
it's not so bad.


